&lt;p&gt;Compensation awarded to successful candidates will vary based on their work location, relevant skills, and experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-slate-node=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-leaf=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-string=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Our total compensation package also includes the opportunity to receive benefits, restricted stock units, and may include incentive compensation.&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-slate-node=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-leaf=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-string=&quot;true&quot;&gt;To learn more about our comprehensive benefit offerings, please check out&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;slate-link selected&quot; href=&quot;https://airtable.com/careers/life-at-airtable&quot; data-slate-node=&quot;element&quot; data-slate-inline=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-node=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-leaf=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-string=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Life at Airtable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span data-slate-node=&quot;text&quot; data-slate-fragment=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-leaf=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-string=&quot;true&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;For work locations in the San Francisco Bay Area, Seattle, New York City, and Los Angeles, the base salary range for this role is:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$196,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$339,900 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please see our Privacy Notice for details regarding Airtable’s collection and use of personal information relating to the application and recruitment process by clicking&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.airtable.com/company/personnel-privacy-notice&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://drive.google.com/file/d/1fKEf0G59m8RT2ZaOJyxoqQ3kW3oUaxhZ/view&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;🔒 &lt;strong&gt;Stay Safe from Job Scams&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;All official Airtable communication will come from an &lt;strong&gt;@airtable.com&lt;/strong&gt; email address. We will never ask you to share sensitive information or purchase equipment during the hiring process. If in doubt, contact us at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:hr@airtable.com&quot;&gt;hr@airtable.com&lt;/a&gt;. Learn more about avoiding job scams &lt;a href=&quot;https://consumer.ftc.gov/consumer-alerts/2022/05/want-work-home-spot-scams-first&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Airtable is the no-code app platform that empowers people closest to the work to accelerate their most critical business processes. More than 500,000 organizations, including 80% of the Fortune 100, rely on Airtable to transform how work gets done.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;mb1&quot;&gt;Airtable&#39;s Brand and Creative team is looking for a Creative Producer to lead operations and production across our creative workstreams. This role sits at the center of how creative work gets done — managing project flow, building stakeholder relationships, and ensuring the right talent is matched to the most important work.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;mb1&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll spend half your time managing complex, concurrent projects and the other half consulting with partners across marketing, product, and engineering to continuously strengthen the collaboration model. You&#39;ll be the person who can see around corners, anticipate bottlenecks, and articulate when priorities need to shift based on strategic realities or resource constraints.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;mb1&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;mb1&quot;&gt;This is not a reactive role. Success means our partners know how to work with us effectively, see us as strategic thought partners, and consistently deliver briefs with clear strategic insights. It means our internal team — a mix of staff, contractors, and agency partners — has clarity on what they&#39;re working on, how projects interconnect, and what it takes to deliver.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage project intake, workflow, and delivery across multiple complex workstreams running simultaneously — web experimentation and optimization, organic social, video production, performance marketing, large-scale events, corporate communications, and more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build relationships with stakeholders across marketing, product, and engineering to understand their goals and continuously improve collaboration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consult on incoming requests to strengthen brief quality and strategic alignment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and advance our Airtable operations app (experience building interfaces and formula logic is a strong plus)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate a dozen+ staff, contractors, and agency partners to match capabilities to project requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage vendor relationships, onboarding, and contract evaluation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan creative capacity and surface conflicts or resource gaps early&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigate competing priorities and help teams understand trade-offs when strategic direction or resources require adjustment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who you are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7-10 years in creative production and operations with in-house experience (agency background is a plus)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiar with the disciplines required to launch campaigns, products, and events — visual design, web, copy, social, video, motion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable using Airtable and capable of building within it; eager to learn more complex automations and integrations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follows AI developments in the creative and advertising industry with genuine interest, knowing how and when to apply them as a complement to human creativity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective at managing multiple creative disciplines and complex workflows simultaneously&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled at stakeholder management across functions and levels, from individual contributors through leadership including VP Design, VP Marketing, as well as Product and Engineering leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-directed and adaptable — you don&#39;t wait for marching orders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Someone who builds influence through expertise and relationships, driving outcomes through collaboration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Airtable is an equal opportunity employer. We embrace diversity and strive to create a workplace where everyone has an equal opportunity to thrive. We welcome people of different backgrounds, experiences, abilities, and perspectives. All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, sex, sexual orientation, gender identity, national origin, disability, protected veteran status or any characteristic protected by applicable federal and state laws, regulations and ordinances. Learn more about your &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://drive.google.com/file/d/1jAj2by1bto5g8Xqn9hWNAwPOMGNd_fM6/view?usp=sharing&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;EEO rights as an applicant&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;VEVRAA-Federal Contractor&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;If you have a medical condition, disability, or religious belief/practice which inhibits your ability to participate in any part of the application or interview process, please complete our &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://airtable.com/shrq13fCV8h1sx2t8&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Accommodations Request Form&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;and let us know how we may assist you. Airtable is committed to participating in the interactive process and providing reasonable accommodations to qualified applicants.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Compensation awarded to successful candidates will vary based on their work location, relevant skills, and experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-slate-node=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-leaf=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-string=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Our total compensation package also includes the opportunity to receive benefits, restricted stock units, and may include incentive compensation.&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-slate-node=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-leaf=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-string=&quot;true&quot;&gt;To learn more about our comprehensive benefit offerings, please check out&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;slate-link selected&quot; href=&quot;https://airtable.com/careers/life-at-airtable&quot; data-slate-node=&quot;element&quot; data-slate-inline=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-node=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-leaf=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-string=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Life at Airtable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span data-slate-node=&quot;text&quot; data-slate-fragment=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-leaf=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-slate-string=&quot;true&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;For work locations in the San Francisco Bay Area, Seattle, New York City, and Los Angeles, the base salary range for this role is:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$192,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$271,900 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please see our Privacy Notice for details regarding Airtable’s collection and use of personal information relating to the application and recruitment process by clicking&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.airtable.com/company/personnel-privacy-notice&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://drive.google.com/file/d/1fKEf0G59m8RT2ZaOJyxoqQ3kW3oUaxhZ/view&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;🔒 &lt;strong&gt;Stay Safe from Job Scams&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;All official Airtable communication will come from an &lt;strong&gt;@airtable.com&lt;/strong&gt; email address. We will never ask you to share sensitive information or purchase equipment during the hiring process. If in doubt, contact us at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:hr@airtable.com&quot;&gt;hr@airtable.com&lt;/a&gt;. Learn more about avoiding job scams &lt;a href=&quot;https://consumer.ftc.gov/consumer-alerts/2022/05/want-work-home-spot-scams-first&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Our mission at Duolingo is to develop the best education in the world and make it universally available. It’s a big mission, and that’s where you come in!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Duolingo, you’ll join a team that cares about educating our users, experimenting with big ideas, making fact-based decisions, and finding innovative solutions to complex problems. You’ll have limitless learning opportunities and daily collaborations with world-class minds — while doing work that’s both meaningful and fun.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join our life-changing mission to develop education for our half a billion (and growing!) learners around the world.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Read &lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.duolingo.com/?utm_source=greenhouse.com&amp;amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;amp;utm_campaign=generalblog_gh_091224&quot;&gt;our blog&lt;/a&gt; to learn more.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us to build Duolingo Ads, Duolingo’s direct ad business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Duolingo is used by over 120 million users every month to learn a language, music, math, or chess. The vast majority of our learners engage with the free, ad-supported version of our app, which is core to our mission of delivering a learning experience that is accessible to all.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As our reach continues to grow, we want to elevate Duolingo’s free experience by introducing higher-quality ad formats that delight learners and offer substantial monetization potential for Duolingo.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an Ad Sales Lead to scale our direct ad business, Duolingo Ads. As a founding member of our sales team, you&#39;ll play a key role in developing Duolingo’s ad strategy while scaling revenue in a priority U.S. region. You’ll collaborate closely with our Business, Monetization, Product, and Design teams to formulate strategies for innovative ad formats that excite advertisers while building on Duolingo’s tenets of gamification, delightful design, brand equity, and character IP.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role reports into our Head of Ad Sales, where you will work in a high-velocity environment to scale revenue by building on Duolingo Ads&#39; foundation, leveraging your extensive network to generate demand and drive value to Duolingo and our advertising partners. This position offers a unique, early-stage opportunity to play a pivotal part in shaping the trajectory of ads on Duolingo for hundreds of millions of learners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://i.ibb.co/JB9S2cD/icon-brain-16px.png&quot; alt=&quot;icon-brain-16px&quot; width=&quot;17&quot; data-is360=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; You will...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop the revenue strategy for your region, aligning with our mission, business objectives, and product guardrail to maintain a high-quality free user experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have input on Duolingo’s “ad menu” and rate cards, identifying standard and native formats that drive value for our advertisers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive revenue growth by generating demand within key verticals and maintaining a pipeline of new and existing advertising clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and implement efficient, repeatable sales strategies and operational processes, prioritizing accounts and managing key relationships effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor market trends and perform competitive analyses to inform strategic decisions and identify emerging opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create compelling sales presentations and proposals using internal and external data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Duolingo at relevant industry events, showcasing our product and expanding our network&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img id=&quot;geom_inter_1726854542099_26_1&quot; class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://i.ibb.co/0F2Z121/icon-check-16px.png&quot; alt=&quot;icon-check-16px&quot; width=&quot;17&quot; data-is360=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; You have...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years of experience in direct ad sales, preferably with a focus on innovative formats and delightful user experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Early stage sales success with experience thriving in ambiguity and creating GTM playbooks from scratch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record in building a book of business of top-tier advertisers in your region&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of the ad tech and mobile app ecosystems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of the Duolingo product and experience working directly with product, engineers, and designers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise in using data to derive insights and assess the performance of ad campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience negotiating and structuring standard and innovative ad buying agreements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional communication and presentation skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to engage C-suite while also rolling up your sleeves to build sales collateral, troubleshoot issues, and directly bring in revenue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to handle multiple projects simultaneously in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Entrepreneurial attitude that favors starting things from scratch, reducing complexity, and quickly testing and reiterating on ideas and processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We post a multi-level salary range for all of our roles.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This is not inclusive of the rest of our awesome portfolio that includes equity compensation and world-class benefits. Our salary ranges are the same for all US locations. Your recruiter can share more details about the range for a specific level during the hiring process. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;The actual salary within the range is determined by many factors including but not limited to, skills, experience, education, and internal equity.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Salary Range: &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$136,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$204,000 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;Z7ph2&quot;&gt;Take a peek at how we care for our employees&#39; holistic well-being with our benefits&lt;a class=&quot;Z7ph2&quot; href=&quot;https://careers.duolingo.com/#benefits&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;Z7ph2&quot;&gt;We will do everything we can within reason to make sure that your interview takes place in an environment that fairly and accurately assesses your skills. If you need assistance or accommodation, please contact&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;Z7ph2&quot; href=&quot;mailto:accommodations@duolingo.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;mailto:accommodations@duolingo.com&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;accommodations@duolingo.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;Z7ph2&quot;&gt;Duolingo is proud to be an Equal Employment Opportunity employer. We do not discriminate based upon race, religion, color, national origin, gender (including pregnancy, childbirth, or related medical conditions), sexual orientation, gender identity, gender expression, age, status as a protected veteran, status as an individual with a disability, or other applicable legally protected characteristics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;Z7ph2&quot;&gt;By applying for this position your data will be processed as per the&lt;a class=&quot;Z7ph2&quot; href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/document/d/e/2PACX-1vTX9GKeRMOMA9Vtm0vfGibrYPYz8ysl0Dg8KSXgj_PxeT5ChsdnNZZWtpxu4t7xillTPGnngnKCjIbV/pub&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Duolingo Applicant Privacy Notice&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
